{"tid":2024754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第卅捌期牆紙】 扭曲","createTime":"2020-05-19T22:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T16:18:00.000Z","uid":253119,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb9830533dc907fc2af225c70539458f7f5e24d","tid":2024754,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T22:02:06.000Z","msg":"「我哭的是一個被扭曲的時代，在那時代行進中被扭曲的人性。」&mdash;&mdash;《行走的樹》<br />\n<br />\n扭曲的制度，在這崩壞的時代裡指鹿為馬：科學權威因政權滲透而扭曲；教育試題被政治批鬥；內會權力被強行褫奪⋯⋯林鄭月娥告訴世界，這是「香港的真相」。<br />\n<br />\n權力伸出利爪，企圖作全方位施壓與威嚇。然而，請擦亮眼睛，牢記這片土地、這個年代中，一頁又一頁的荒唐歷史。願我們一起，以真相對抗這荒唐的時代，永遠不作滿嘴謊言的傀儡。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 傷害國民感情利大於弊 <br />\n2. 習森科主義<br />\n3. 西客宣言<br />\n4. 權力多面睇：香港反送中運動全透析<br />\n5. 結業黃店的倔強與溫柔<br />\n6. 理想與寫實主義之爭&mdash;&mdash;黃頭盔的象徵意義<br />\n7. Two Approaches to Bargaining: Democratisation in the late 20th Century<br />\n8. Until Tyranny Is Defeated, Hong Kong Must Stand<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#38期 #38th<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWtCGA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWtCGA2.jpg&h=986ebaf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1Q9xHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1Q9xHJ.jpg&h=a94eea9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zoCGA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zoCGA4.jpg&h=27657bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXqJB9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXqJB9q.jpg&h=fd660d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cRwHSHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRwHSHM.jpg&h=757c47a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZH